"Story\nThe world is in danger from an unknown force that has caused a massive blackout, stranding people across the globe in complete darkness. The main character - an engineer, pilot, and survivalist - must traverse a hostile world in search of answers, using his skills and ingenuity to stay one step ahead of the unknown threat. As he encounters other survivors, he learns that the source of the blackout is a powerful machine located deep in the heart of a massive mountain range. The players must race against the clock to disable the machine and restore power across the world, all while avoiding the hostile world around them."